{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cb40d67e-1fc8-4d8a-b7fb-c2b791dd698e","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n## 1. Project file — `YourTests.csproj`\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.7\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net9.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\n`MSTest.Sdk` bundles MSTest runner, assertions, and the test framework — no extra `<PackageReference>` needed.\n\n## 2. Enable parallel execution — `.runsettings`\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>          <!-- 0 = use all logical processors -->\n      <Scope>Class</Scope>          <!-- parallelize at class level -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nWire it up in the csproj (inside `<PropertyGroup>`):\n\n```xml\n<TestRunSettingsFile>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\.runsettings</TestRunSettingsFile>\n```\n\n## 3. Sequential database tests — use `[DoNotParallelize]`\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]                // runs sequentially, never overlaps with other tests\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Can_Insert_Record() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Can_Read_Back_Record() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- `[DoNotParallelize]` on a class excludes **all its methods** from parallel execution and runs them one-at-a-time after parallel tests finish.\n- You can also put it on individual `[TestMethod]`s for finer control.\n- `Scope=\"Class\"` means different test classes run in parallel but methods within a class are sequential — a safe default for shared per-class fixtures.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"e2f18d89-aaf2-47d8-a1eb-39dd31cbaad7","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The directory is empty. The user is asking for guidance on setting up a new MSTest project. Let me provide the recommended setup based on my knowledge of MSTest.Sdk.","outputTokens":533,"requestId":"EBC5:1F9B94:7CEEBE:85018F:6A044F0D"},"id":"78a0726a-7cad-45e0-9b03-06d120454e8d","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:14:51.415Z","parentId":"509942a7-d3b7-4f8e-abaa-c3c028968ac4"}
